    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation evidence demonstrates NIH prediction error of 7.3% against FDA benchmark data, within the 10% acceptance criterion. RH index < 1 at all five COU operating points satisfies the primary regulatory acceptance criterion. The model is accepted as sufficiently credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
